Package: stoppingrule
Type: Package
Title: Create and Evaluate Stopping Rules
Version: 0.2.0
Author: Michael J. Martens <mmartens@mcw.edu>
Maintainer: Michael J. Martens <mmartens@mcw.edu>
Description: Provides functions for creating, displaying, and evaluating stopping rules for safety monitoring in clinical studies. Implements stopping rule methods described in Goldman (1987) <doi:10.1016/0197-2456(87)90153-X>; Geller et al. (2003, ISBN:9781135524388); Ivanova, Qaqish, and Schell (2005) <doi:10.1111/j.1541-0420.2005.00311.x>; Chen and Chaloner (2006) <doi.org/10.1002/sim.2429>; and Kulldorff et al. (2011) <doi:10.1080/07474946.2011.539924>.
Imports: stats, utils
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 7.1.1
